ABOUT
OUR STORY
Whiskey Row has been serving customers in Melbourne, FL and surrounding areas for years. Our mission is to serve the most delicious food and refreshing drinks so that we become your number one bar & lounge of choice. We are committed to high quality service and making sure you have an amazing visit.
You’ll love our signature cocktails and happy hour specials. Many customers come here to relax, escape daily stresses, and also reconnect with friends and loved ones. At Whiskey Row, we do more than just serve food and drinks. We also pride ourselves in being a cool local hang out spot. We have Dart Boards, Shuffleboard, The latest version of Golden Tee, and Pool Tables.
Free Pool on Saturday and Sunday, All Day!
We encourage you to explore our website, view our menu and most importantly, give us a try. If you have any questions or concerns, please don't hesitate to contact us. We look forward to hearing from you.

PRIVATE EVENTS
Host Your Next Event at
WHISKEY ROW
Do you have an upcoming birthday or other special occasion to celebrate? Looking to entertain clients or get together with friends? You’ll love the chill and relaxing vibes here at Whiskey Row. We know that while you may have plenty of other bars and lounges to consider in and near Melbourne, very few places can compare to the atmosphere, food, drinks, and level of service at Whiskey Row.
We offer several private party packages to choose from and can even create a custom menu to accommodate your needs. Feel free to browse our menu and view some of our offerings and don't hesitate to contact us. One of our event experts will be happy to assist you and answer any questions you may have.
Contact Us
